1. make files
   (copies the source files to \plplot\tmp)
2. make win3 or make bgi
   (creates pldevs.h and plconfig.h and a makefile in \plplot\tmp)
3. cd \plplot\tmp
   make (this creates the library : plplotl.lib or plplotwl.lib)
   e.g. make x01c to make an example

